description:
Int. demo & conversion of  existing restaurant for new tenant, Miller's Ale 
House
Interior renovations 1st, 2nd, 3rd floors as per plans
Convert existing screened porch in to a heated year round room
Remove old front stairs and replace with new, same dimensions

3rd Fl: install skylights in attic for future bedroom suite, insulate rafter space 
w/spray foam; rough in elec/plumbing

Kitchen/bathroom renovations 1st/2nd floors; replace windows; new furnace 
to install radiant heat all floors

1st Fl: Kitchen remodel, renovate 1/2 bath; 2nd Fl: renovate 2 baths, new 
stair treads &  misc. finish work
Trench - excavation for foundation & on-site utilities site work
RAZE free standing garage/barn which has been condemned;

Basement: plumbing repairs; 2nd Fl: finish off exist. Walk-up second floor 
attic for 1 additional 1/2 bath & 1 bedroom by an 8' dormer

1st Fl: kitchen remodel: demo of all horse hair plaster; insulate; new drywall, 
kitchen cabinets

1st Fl: redo kitchen cabinets; 2nd Fl: redo bath fixtures, move tub & add 
laundry closet

Close off existing front porch to create a mudroom; add open porch 23'x 
16'
Excavation and foundation for new 44-unit apartment building

1st Fl: front porch repairs, stairs, deck, 2 new footings (same dimensions 
6' x 12')
Trench - excavation for foundation & on-site utilities site work
Construct new 12'6"x12'6" mudroom addition with 1/2 bath
1ST Fl: repairs to front porch: remove & replace rotted material

Replace front stairs &  railing; lally column & replace front porch to same 
dimensions
2nd Floor Bath - replace subfloor, tile & walls
Cover old siding with new vinyl siding
Remove existing roofing shingles, sister joist, if needed
Trench - Relocating of retaining wall by 5' to expand driveway
Strip& reroof; 6' Ice, water Arch. Shingles

New construction of 2 buildings: parcel 1 - 135 res. Units & assoc. pkg; 
parcel 2: 35 res. Units , 1100 sf retail & assoc. pkg.
1st fl kitchen remodel; demo 2 partition walls; new windows

Demo porch & construct FOUNDATION only for new addition as per 
plans
Remove & replace front porches 1st/2nd floors, same dimensions 7' x 27'
Closed cell spray foam insulation in attic
Construct new addition to rear of house
